# Live trading runtime files: KEPT in git so future Claude sessions and the
# scheduled GitHub Action see the running state. The Action commits these
# back after each run.
# (No exclusion needed — everything in data/processed/live/ is tracked.)

# Keep directory markers so the layout reproduces on fresh clone
!data/raw/.gitkeep
!data/processed/.gitkeep

